name: Xing Zhan Qing Yuan
overview: Xing Zhan Qing Yuan (alternative and lesser quality releases named Wai Xing Zhan Shi, Xing He Zhan Shi, and Xing Ji Zheng Ba) are all the same port of Phantasy Star IV for the Famicom. They seem to have been released at different stages of development, with the Xing Zhan Qing Yuan version having a lot more features and better art and music.
